WEBVTT

00:08:59.754 --> 00:09:02.609
naturally part of a human spectrum

00:09:02.633 --> 00:09:04.577
and not as defects.

00:09:04.601 --> 00:09:07.910
And this is something
that I agree to completely.

00:09:08.903 --> 00:09:13.450
If autism was seen as part
of a natural human spectrum,

00:09:13.474 --> 00:09:20.069
then the world could be designed
to work better for autistic people.

00:09:20.728 --> 00:09:23.450
I am not ashamed of my autism.

00:09:24.188 --> 00:09:27.188
And I may not think like you,

00:09:27.212 --> 00:09:28.887
or act like you,

00:09:28.911 --> 00:09:32.124
but I am still human
and I am not diseased.